description: S73 application seeking variation of conditions 2 (approved plans) and 3 (approved documents) of planning permission ref. 66819/APP/2014/1600 dated 24th December 2014 for:  Redevelopment of the site to provide a foodstore with ancillary cafe (Class A1) and ancillary petrol filling station, cinema (Class D2), 5 x restaurant units (Class A3), and residential development consisting of 132 units, together with new vehicle and pedestrian accesses, car parking, servicing areas, landscaping arrangements, and other associated works.  Changes sought: 1) Increase of total units on the site from 132 to 163 and associated design/ elevation changes. 2) Changes to the approved Energy Strategy.
